            <p>Organizations that receive Shingo recognition fall into three categories:</p>
            <ul class="square">
                <li><strong>Shingo Prize</strong> - a worldwide recognized symbol of an organization’s successful establishment
                    of a culture anchored on principles of enterprise excellence</li>
                <li><strong>Shingo Silver Medallion</strong> - organizations maturing on the journey with primary focus on tools
                    and systems for improvement</li>
                <li><strong>Shingo Bronze Medallion</strong> – organizations in the earlier stages of cultural transformation
                    with primary focus on tools for improvement</li>
            </ul>
